data.description:
A Country Setting provides this vintage  home with naturally beautiful surroundings rarely found.
The neighbor's pastureland sprinkled with roaming cattle capture a peaceful and tranquil atmosphere.
Located at the end of a col-d-sac, This two-bedroom, two-bath home is delightfully arranged for the flow of family life and fun.  The Open Kitchen is connected to the living room by an elegant double-sided bar.  From the Living area there is a Game Room with floor-to-ceiling windows overlooking the caged in-ground pool, and a covered area for out-door entertainment and relaxation, The bedrooms are located at the east end together with a hall-way bonus room and a large multi-purpose bonus room  having windows on three sides giving plenty of light and a view of All Out Doors. This room needs  painting and floor covering left for Buyer's choice after occupancy with no Seller participation. The Double Garage contains the laundry area, complete with Laundry Tub and Storage cabinets around the walls. There is  a retractable screen door for air flow and easy-access. The  air conditioning system and duct work  were recently professionally cleaned and sanitized.  
 Elf Drive leads to Sparta Road, a connecting artery to both SR 66 and US 27. From there it is just a 
few blocks away from Shopping, Restaurants, and many other options.  Property being offered "AS IS" with inspections welcome at Buyer's option.
